{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775842061146,"sessionID":"ses_28790d8f7ffeVNEFllz282kAwQ","part":{"id":"prt_d786f6566001brvnvIFaWs1JYF","messageID":"msg_d786f437f001kxZCbvq2brr2RE","sessionID":"ses_28790d8f7ffeVNEFllz282kAwQ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 Design: CRD Shared Types and Constants (client-go)\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: **AR ID:** AR-003  \n6: **Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n7: **Language:** Go  \n8: **Size:** Small  \n9: \n10: Generate the Kubernetes client-go library for the API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`. The generated client provides programmatic access to `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` CRDs, including typed clients, informers, and listers.\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Architecture\n15: \n16: ### High-Level Design\n17: \n18: The client-go library follows the standard Kubernetes code-generation pattern, providing a layered architecture for interacting with custom resources:\n19: \n20: ```\n21: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n22: │                           Consumer Applications                              │\n23: │  ┌───────────────┐  ┌───────────────┐  ┌───────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐ │\n24: │  │   Controllers │  │    CLI Tools  │  │  Workload Mgr │  │   Test Mocks │ │\n25: │  └───────┬───────┘  └───────┬───────┘  └───────┬───────┘  └──────┬───────┘ │\n26: └──────────┼──────────────────┼──────────────────┼─────────────────┼─────────┘\n27:            │                  │                  │                 │\n28:            ▼                  ▼                  ▼                 ▼\n29: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n30: │                           client-go Library                                  │\n31: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n32: │  │                        Clientset (Interface)                          │   │\n33: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │   │\n34: │  │  │                    RuntimeV1alpha1Interface                     │  │   │\n35: │  │  │  ┌─────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────────────────┐  │  │   │\n36: │  │  │  │ AgentRuntimeInterface│  │    CodeInterpreterInterface     │  │  │   │\n37: │  │  │  │ · Create()          │  │  · Create()                     │  │  │   │\n38: │  │  │  │ · Get()             │  │  · Get()                        │  │  │   │\n39: │  │  │  │ · List()            │  │  · List()                       │  │  │   │\n40: │  │  │  │ · Watch()           │  │  · Watch()                      │  │  │   │\n41: │  │  │  │ · Update()          │  │  · Update()                     │  │  │   │\n42: │  │  │  │ · UpdateStatus()    │  │  · UpdateStatus()               │  │  │   │\n43: │  │  │  │ · Delete()          │  │  · Delete()                     │  │  │   │\n44: │  │  │  │ · Patch()           │  │  · Patch()                      │  │  │   │\n45: │  │  │  └─────────────────────┘  └─────────────────────────────────┘  │  │   │\n46: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │   │\n47: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n48: │                                                                              │\n49: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n50: │  │                     SharedInformerFactory                             │   │\n51: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │   │\n52: │  │  │  ┌─────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────────────────┐  │  │   │\n53: │  │  │  │ AgentRuntimeInformer│  │    CodeInterpreterInformer      │  │  │   │\n54: │  │  │  │ · Informer()        │  │  · Informer()                   │  │  │   │\n55: │  │  │  │ · Lister()          │  │  · Lister()                     │  │  │   │\n56: │  │  │  └─────────────────────┘  └─────────────────────────────────┘  │  │   │\n57: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │   │\n58: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n59: │                                                                              │\n60: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n61: │  │                      Lister Interfaces                                │   │\n62: │  │  ┌─────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────────────────┐        │   │\n63: │  │  │ AgentRuntimeLister  │  │    CodeInterpreterLister        │        │   │\n64: │  │  │ · List()            │  │  · List()                       │        │   │\n65: │  │  │ · AgentRuntimes()   │  │  · CodeInterpreters()           │        │   │\n66: │  │  │   (namespace lister)│  │    (namespace lister)           │        │   │\n67: │  │  └─────────────────────┘  └─────────────────────────────────┘        │   │\n68: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n69: │                                                                              │\n70: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n71: │  │                    Scheme / Codecs (register.go)                      │   │\n72: │  │  · AddToScheme()  · Scheme  · Codecs  · ParameterCodec               │   │\n73: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n74: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n75: ```\n76: \n77: ### Component Interactions\n78: \n79: | Component | Purpose | Input | Output |\n80: |-----------|---------|-------|--------|\n81: | **Clientset** | Entry point for all API operations | `*rest.Config` | Typed clients per group-version |\n82: | **Typed Client** | CRUD operations for specific resource | Context, resource object | Result object, error |\n83: | **Informer** | Watch and cache resources | Client, resync period | `cache.SharedIndexInformer` |\n84: | **Lister** | Read-only cached access | Label selectors | Cached resource list |\n85: | **Scheme** | Type registration and serialization | Raw bytes/Objects | Typed objects |\n86: \n87: ---\n88: \n89: ## Data Structures\n90: \n91: ### Clientset\n92: \n93: #### Interface Definition\n94: \n95: ```go\n96: // Interface provides access to the AgentCube API clientset.\n97: type Interface interface {\n98:     Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n99:     RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n100: }\n101: ```\n102: \n103: #### Clientset Struct\n104: \n105: ```go\n106: // Clientset contains the clients for groups. Each group has exactly one\n107: // version included in a Clientset.\n108: type Clientset struct {\n109:     *discovery.DiscoveryClient\n110:     runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client\n111: }\n112: ```\n113: \n114: #### Constructors\n115: \n116: | Function | Signature | Description |\n117: |----------|-----------|-------------|\n118: | `NewForConfig` | `func(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)` | Creates clientset from REST config |\n119: | `NewForConfigAndClient` | `func(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)` | Creates with custom HTTP client |\n120: | `NewForConfigOrDie` | `func(c *rest.Config) *Clientset` | Creates or panics on error |\n121: | `New` | `func(c rest.Interface) *Clientset` | Creates from REST interface |\n122: \n123: ### Typed Client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\n124: \n125: #### RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n126: \n127: ```go\n128: // RuntimeV1alpha1Interface provides access to runtime/v1alpha1 resources.\n129: type RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n130:     RESTClient() rest.Interface\n131:     AgentRuntimesGetter\n132:     CodeInterpretersGetter\n133: }\n134: ```\n135: \n136: #### AgentRuntimesGetter / AgentRuntimeInterface\n137: \n138: ```go\n139: // AgentRuntimesGetter provides access to AgentRuntime resources.\n140: type AgentRuntimesGetter interface {\n141:     AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n142: }\n143: \n144: // AgentRuntimeInterface provides CRUD operations for AgentRuntime resources.\n145: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n146:     Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n147:     Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n148:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n149:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n150:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n151:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n152:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n153:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n154:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n155:     AgentRuntimeExpansion\n156: }\n157: ```\n158: \n159: **REST Resource:** `agentruntimes` (plural)\n160: \n161: #### CodeInterpretersGetter / CodeInterpreterInterface\n162: \n163: ```go\n164: // CodeInterpretersGetter provides access to CodeInterpreter resources.\n165: type CodeInterpretersGetter interface {\n166:     CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n167: }\n168: \n169: // CodeInterpreterInterface provides CRUD operations for CodeInterpreter resources.\n170: type CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n171:     Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n172:     Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n173:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n174:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n175:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n176:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n177:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList, error)\n178:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n179:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n180:     CodeInterpreterExpansion\n181: }\n182: ```\n183: \n184: **REST Resource:** `codeinterpreters` (plural)\n185: \n186: #### Expansion Hooks\n187: \n188: ```go\n189: // AgentRuntimeExpansion allows adding custom methods to AgentRuntimeInterface.\n190: type AgentRuntimeExpansion interface{}\n191: \n192: // CodeInterpreterExpansion allows adding custom methods to CodeInterpreterInterface.\n193: type CodeInterpreterExpansion interface{}\n194: ```\n195: \n196: ### Scheme\n197: \n198: #### Package: `clientset/versioned/scheme/`\n199: \n200: ```go\n201: // Package scheme contains the scheme registration for the runtime/v1alpha1 API group.\n202: 