atform.\n\n## API Group\n\n- Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`\n\n## Shared Types\n\n### Common Phase Types\n\nDefine common phase enums that can be reused across CRDs.\n\n### Common Condition Types\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","time":{"start":1775842061114,"end":1775842061149}}}}
