e `SecretKeySelector` type (for referencing secrets)\n44: - [ ] Define `ConfigMapKeySelector` type (for referencing configmaps)\n45: - [ ] Define `LocalObjectReference` type (for simple object references)\n46: - [ ] Add JSON tags using camelCase naming\n47: \n48: ---\n49: \n50: ## Task 5: Update register.go\n51: **Verifiable Output:** Shared types registered in scheme\n52: \n53: - [ ] Ensure shared types are properly registered\n54: - [ ] Update scheme builder if needed\n55: - [ ] Verify AddToScheme includes shared types\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ## Task 6: Generate DeepCopy Methods\n60: **Verifiable Output:** `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` contains DeepCopy methods for shared types\n61: \n62: - [ ] Run `controller-gen object:headerFile=\"hack/boilerplate.go.txt\" paths=\"./...\"`\n63: - [ ] Verify `DeepCopyInto`, `DeepCopy`, `DeepCopyObject` methods generated for shared types\n64: - [ ] Verify DeepCopy methods generated for all shared structs\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ## Task 7: Verify Compilation\n69: **Verifiable Output:** `go build` succeeds without errors\n70: \n71: - [ ] Run `go build ./pkg/apis/...`\n72: - [ ] Verify no compilation errors\n73: - [ ] Verify no type definition errors\n74: \n75: ---\n76: \n77: ## Task 8: Verify Import Compatibility\n78: **Verifiable Output:** Shared types can be imported by AR-001 and AR-002\n79: \n80: - [ ] Verify AR-001 types can import shared types\n81: - [ ] Verify AR-002 types can import shared types\n82: - [ ] Check for any circular dependency issues\n83: \n84: ---\n85: \n86: ## Task 9: Run Unit Tests\n87: **Verifiable Output:** All existing tests pass\n88: \n89: - [ ] Run `go test ./pkg/apis/...`\n90: - [ ] Verify no test failures\n91: \n92: ---\n93: \n94: ## Completion Criteria\n95: \n96: - [ ] All tasks 1-9 completed\n97: - [ ] Code follows project naming conventions (PascalCase structs, camelCase JSON tags)\n98: - [ ] Shared types are properly documented\n99: - [ ] Constants have descriptive comments\n100: - [ ] Compatible with AR-001 and AR-002 patterns\n\n(End of file - total 100 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 Tasks: CRD Shared Types and Constants\n\n> **Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n> **Language:** Go  \n> **Size:** S  \n> **Stage:** open\n\n---\n\n## Task 1: Define Common Phase Types\n**Verifiable Output:** Shared phase types defined in `common_types.go`\n\n- [ ] Define `RuntimePhase` enum type\n- [ ] Define phase constants (Pending, Running, Succeeded, Failed, Unknown)\n- [ ] Add JSON tags using camelCase naming\n- [ ] Add kubebuilder validation markers\n\n---\n\n## Task 2: Define Shared Condition Types","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775842061121,"end":1775842061151}}}}
